# 🧠 RECOMMENDED FUTURE SYSTEMS

You don’t need these immediately, but this is the correct direction:

| System        | Purpose             |
| ------------- | ------------------- |
| AssetImporter | imports files       |
| AssetRegistry | stores definitions  |
| AssetBrowser  | creator UI          |
| AssetResolver | runtime lookup      |
| AssetPackager | export/build system |

That is the real creator-platform pipeline.

